cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote S address to an unreachable IP (10.0.0.1) prevents the CU from connecting to the DU via the F1 interface, resulting in F1 setup failure.

du.explanation_en: Altering the uplink timing advance parameters (T1a_cp_ul) causes inconsistency with downlink timing, leading to improper timing synchronization and potential data transmission errors.
